node.title: Search for clues in the investigation into Cleo Smith's abduction far from over
node.alt: The house where Cleo Smith was found in Carnarvon.
node.description: Forensic police officers at the centre of the investigation into Cleo Smith's abduction are expected to spend at least the next week at the Carnarvon house where she was found.
node.content:
["Police forensic investigators are expected to spend at least the next week, if not longer, at the Carnarvon house where four-year-old Cleo Smith was found.", "There has been a large police presence at the Tonkin Crescent home since detectives forced their way inside early on Wednesday morning.", "Officers\u00a0wearing blue plastic forensic suits, masks, and gloves continue to work inside the home, and detectives in their suits come and go regularly.", "Meanwhile, uniformed officers stand guard and make sure that children playing in the park over the road do not run beneath the police tape bordering the crime scene.", "", "
Police are expected to remain at the scene for a week or longer.(ABC News: James Carmody)
", "One of the police cars outside of the home still bears one of the missing child bumper stickers that were plastered on vehicles throughout the region.", "Many within the large contingent of detectives sent to Carnarvon flew the 900 kilometres back to Perth yesterday.", "", "
The Carnarvon house where the four-year-old was found is being guarded by police.(ABC News: James Carmody)
", "But they are only home for the weekend and are due to fly back to Carnarvon first thing Monday morning.", "It is understood they will remain in the town for the next three weeks as the investigation continues.", "", "
Officers returning home to Perth for the weekend, are expected to return to Carnarvon on Monday.(ABC News: James Carmody)
", "Meanwhile, the man charged with child stealing, Terence Darrell Kelly, spent Friday night in a maximum-security prison in Perth.", "He was flown out the small town yesterday by four special operations group corrections officers.", "", "
Cleo Smith's alleged abductor Terence Kelly was pictured on social media holding Bratz dolls.\u00a0(Facebook)
", "While in custody in Carnarvon, the 36-year-old was twice taken to the local hospital for what police said were self-inflicted injuries suffered while alone in the cells.", "He is due to appear in court again next month.", "", "
Terence Kelly was flown to Perth on a charter flight out of Carnarvon.(Getty Images: Tamati Smith\u00a0)
"]
